1.1 Install docker
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Official website: https://www.docker.com/
DockerHub: https://hub.docker.com/

Install docker:

	$ curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com/ | sh

Fix permission problem:

	$ sudo usermod -aG docker <username> # logout login to see effect


1.2 Basic
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Start docker daemon:
	$ sudo service docker restart

Pull docker images:
	$ docker pull ubuntu

List all docker images:
	$ docker images

Remove images:
	$ docker rmi image_id

Run docker images:
	$ docker run -it ubuntu

List all docker process:
	$ docker ps

Kill docker process:
	$ docker kill process_id

List all containers:
	$ docker ps -a

Kill all containers:
	$ docker rm `docker ps -aq`

All process status:
	$ docker stats

Attach to container:
	$ docker attach container_id

<c-p><c-q> to dettach


